1. *Poverenje* je temelj svake dobre veze. (Trust is the foundation of any good relationship.)
2. Oni su izgubili *poverenje* u sebe. (They have lost trust in themselves.)
3. Oni su uspeli da izgrade *poverenje* između sebe. (They have managed to build trust between them.)
4. *Poveriti* smo sebe da možemo da ostvarimo svoje snove. (We trust ourselves to be able to achieve our dreams.)
5. *Poverenje* je bitno za uspešno preduzetništvo. (Trust is important for successful entrepreneurship.)